<i>adjective</i>: 버석하다 [버서카다], 버석버석하다 [버석뻐서카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>버석하다 [버서카다]</dt><br>
<dd>crisp; crumbly; friable</dd><br>
<dd>너무 말라서 잘게 부스러질 만큼 물기가 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>So dry without moisture as to crumble into small pieces.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>버석버석하다 [버석뻐서카다]</dt><br>
<dd>crisp; crumbly; friable</dd><br>
<dd>너무 말라서 잘게 부스러질 만큼 물기가 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>So dry without moisture as to crumble into small pieces.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>